data.description:
Back on the market! First time home buyer never did inspections! Now is your chance to
Step into luxury with this captivating two-story colonial, tucked away in a serene cul-de-sac. With four bedrooms and 3 1/2 bathrooms, the house features beautiful hardwood floors, a formal dining room, and an open concept kitchen. Enjoy the natural light streaming through numerous windows, revealing a patio and a spacious private backyard with 6' privacy fence. The updated kitchen showcases granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a gas range, and ample storage, including a center island for extra seating. Upstairs, four large bedrooms with walk-in closets await, including a primary bedroom with a private office and a luxurious updated master bath. The finished basement adds versatility with a fifth nonconforming bedroom and a full bathroom. Conveniently located near restaurants, shopping, and entertainment, this home offers easy highway access and falls within the Olathe school district. Your perfect haven awaits!
